    "body": "> Yeah, but the issue is there is no way to create role.\r\n\r\nThere is no such thing as creating a role. All roles exist by default, and are administered by the `DEFAULT_ADMIN_ROLE` (`bytes32(0)`).\r\n\r\nYou can grant any role at any time internally (using `_grantRole` and `_revokeRole`). You can also change the role admin using `_setRoleAdmin`.\r\n\r\n",
